<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p><rs type="material">White marble</rs> <rs type="objectType">sarcophagus</rs> lid re-used as a trough (<measure dim="width" type="length" unit="metre">1.965</measure> x <measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.29</measure>  x <measure dim="depth" type="length" unit="metre">0.81</measure>).</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p><rs type="execution" key="scalpro">Inscribed</rs> on the edge of the sarcophagus lid (<measure dim="width" type="length" unit="metre">1.965</measure> x <measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.08</measure>), which is rubbed in places and pierced by several holes; some of the damage was done before the inscription was cut. The text must have continued on the box of the sarcophagus.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Letters</head>
<p><measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.02</measure>; ligatured <foreign lang="grc">MM</foreign>, l. 2.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="date">
<head>Date</head>
<p>
<date exact="none" cert="low" notAfter="0300" notBefore="0201"> Probably third century A.D.</date>
(<rs type="criteria">lettering</rs>).</p>
</div>
