<p> Titus <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> Ailius Zotikos prepared the tomb and the subsidiary niches.  In the tomb his children Philetos and Ammia have been buried but no-one else <supplied reason="lost">shall be placed therein</supplied> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/></p>
